---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ScrollIndicator from '../components/ScrollIndicator.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About EES | Family-Owned Solar & Energy Installer Geelong"
  description="Meet the team behind EES. Family-owned and operated from Moolap, Geelong. CEC accredited solar, battery, heat pump, and energy system specialists with a research lab on site."
>
  <!-- ── Hero: Full-bleed photo with editorial overlay ── -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-hero-bg">
      <img src="/image/photos_EESshed/Aboutus_exterior.webp" alt="EES facility exterior in Moolap, Geelong" />
      <div class="about-hero-overlay"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-hero-content">
      <p class="about-hero-label">About EES</p>
      <h1>A family business<br />built on research,<br />run by <span class="hero-accent">electricians</span></h1>
      <p class="about-hero-sub">Based in Moolap, Geelong. Servicing Greater Geelong, Melbourne &amp; Regional Victoria.</p>
    </div>
    <img src="/image/icon/Brand_wave_dots_white.svg" alt="" class="about-hero-wave" aria-hidden="true" />
  </section>

  <!-- ── Intro strip ── -->
  <section class="intro-strip">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-strip-inner">
        <div class="intro-stat">
          <span class="intro-stat-number">10+</span>
          <span class="intro-stat-label">Years operating<br />in Geelong</span>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-stat">
          <span class="intro-stat-number">5000+</span>
          <span class="intro-stat-label">Panels installed<br />&amp; counting</span>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-stat">
          <span class="intro-stat-number">10yr</span>
          <span class="intro-stat-label">Workmanship<br />warranty</span>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-stat">
          <span class="intro-stat-number">48hr</span>
          <span class="intro-stat-label">Critical fault<br />response time</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Our Story ── -->
  <section class="story-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="story-layout">
        <div class="story-col-left">
          <p class="section-label">Our Story</p>
          <h2>What if a home could<br />heat, cool, and power<br />itself?</h2>
          <p class="story-lead">That question led to the founding of Environmental Energy Services in Moolap, Geelong.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="story-col-right">
          <p>What began as a research project has grown into a full-service energy company with its own laboratory, its own products, and a team of qualified electricians and researchers working under one roof.</p>
          <p>We're not a marketing company that outsources installations. We hold our own REC Electrical Licence. Our team <strong>designs, installs, and supports every system we put in</strong>. Your warranty sits with a real brick-and-mortar business here in Geelong, not a call centre somewhere else.</p>
          <p>We come from a research and academic background. Our founding director, Dr Mark Luther, is an Honorary Professor of Deakin University after 27 years of service. That research-first thinking runs through everything we do, from how we analyse your energy data to how we design your system.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="story-photos">
        <div class="story-photo story-photo--wide">
          <img src="/image/photos_EESshed/Group%20131%20(1).png" alt="EES team members outside the Moolap facility" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="story-photo story-photo--tall">
          <img src="/image/photos_EESshed/Group%20132.png" alt="EES headquarters in Moolap, Geelong" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── What Makes Us Different ── -->
  <section class="difference-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="difference-header">
        <p class="section-label section-label--light">What Makes Us Different</p>
        <h2>We don't just install.<br />We understand your home.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="difference-grid">
        <div class="difference-card">
          <div class="difference-number">01</div>
          <h3>Holistic approach</h3>
          <p>We look at your entire energy picture. Solar, battery, heat pump, hot water, home automation, even whether it's worth disconnecting from gas entirely. Every recommendation connects back to your actual usage and future plans.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="difference-card">
          <div class="difference-number">02</div>
          <h3>Data-driven design</h3>
          <p>We pull your interval metering data down to half-hour increments. We look at where your power goes, when you're using it, and how much your existing system generates. We never guess, and we never oversize to sell you more panels.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="difference-card">
          <div class="difference-number">03</div>
          <h3>Back-to-base monitoring</h3>
          <p>Every system we install is connected to our monitoring portal. Our team checks every system each morning. We've contacted clients about faults before they even knew something was wrong. 48 business hour response for critical issues.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="difference-card">
          <div class="difference-number">04</div>
          <h3>Built for high-end homes</h3>
          <p>50 to 60 percent of our work is in architectural and designed homes. We work directly with architects and builders to run cabling under plaster, match finishes, and make sure your system fits the property, not the other way around.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="difference-card">
          <div class="difference-number">05</div>
          <h3>Honest workmanship warranty</h3>
          <p>We offer a 10-year workmanship warranty. That's double the legal minimum. We've been operating for over a decade and we'll be here long after the rebates expire. No 30-year promises from a company that's been around for one.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="difference-card">
          <div class="difference-number">06</div>
          <h3>Ongoing energy advice</h3>
          <p>We don't disappear after installation. We regularly check in with clients about new electricity plans, VPP opportunities, and ways to get more out of their system. It's advice as a service, not just panels on a roof.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── The Team ── -->
  <section class="team-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="team-header">
        <p class="section-label">The People</p>
        <h2>Meet our team</h2>
        <p class="team-intro">From research to installation to ongoing support, every part of EES is handled in-house by people who know what they're doing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="team-grid">
        <div class="team-card team-card--featured">
          <div class="team-card-photo">
            <img src="/image/photos_team/DrMarkLuther_clean_transparent.png" alt="Dr Mark Luther" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="team-card-info">
            <h3>Dr Mark B. Luther</h3>
            <p class="team-role">Director (Arch.D.)</p>
            <p>Honorary Professor of Deakin University after 27 years of service. Specialises in Architecture Science and Environmental Technology. Inventor of the Environmental Service Pod and the Autonomatic Hydronic Ceiling Panel.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card team-card--featured">
          <div class="team-card-photo">
            <img src="/image/photos_team/LincolnLuther_clean_transparent.png" alt="Lincoln Luther" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="team-card-info">
            <h3>Lincoln B. Luther</h3>
            <p class="team-role">Manager of Sales</p>
            <p>Over 4 years industry experience in renewables with a background in Economics, Banking and Finance. Leads every consultation, system design, and energy analysis. The first person you'll speak to.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card team-card--featured">
          <div class="team-card-photo">
            <img src="/image/photos_team/Matthew Ellison_02_clean_transparent.png" alt="Matthew Ellison" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="team-card-info">
            <h3>Matthew Ellison</h3>
            <p class="team-role">Manager of Installations</p>
            <p>Senior electrician experienced in residential and commercial solar PV and battery installations. Checks every system every morning through back-to-base monitoring. Also involved in research and design on the Environmental Service Pod.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-card-photo">
            <img src="/image/photos_team/HungQDo_clean_transparent.png" alt="Hung Q. Do" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="team-card-info">
            <h3>Hung Q. Do</h3>
            <p class="team-role">Research Development</p>
            <p>PhD candidate specialising in hydronic ceiling innovative systems. His research focuses on effective conditioning through hydronic control in commercial buildings.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-card-photo">
            <img src="/image/photos_team/placeholder.svg" alt="Pat Sandall" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="team-card-info">
            <h3>Pat Sandall</h3>
            <p class="team-role">Head Electrician, A Grade</p>
            <p>A Grade electrician leading EES field installations across solar, battery, and integrated energy systems for residential and commercial projects.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-card-photo">
            <img src="/image/photos_team/placeholder.svg" alt="Caleb Nowson" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="team-card-info">
            <h3>Caleb Nowson</h3>
            <p class="team-role">Business Development Manager</p>
            <p>Manages business development and client relationships, connecting homeowners and businesses with the right energy solutions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Accreditations ── -->
  <section class="accreditations-section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label" style="text-align: center;">Accreditations</p>
      <h2 class="accreditations-heading">Our Credentials</h2>
      <div class="accreditations-logos">
        <div class="accreditation-logo"><img src="/image/_logos_partners/clean-energy-council-member.webp" alt="Clean Energy Council Member" /></div>
        <div class="accreditation-logo"><img src="/image/_logos_partners/cec-approved-seller.webp" alt="CEC Approved Seller" /></div>
        <div class="accreditation-logo"><img src="/image/_logos_partners/solar-accreditation-australia.webp" alt="Solar Accreditation Australia" /></div>
        <div class="accreditation-logo"><img src="/image/_logos_partners/smart-energy-council.webp" alt="Smart Energy Council" /></div>
        <div class="accreditation-logo"><img src="/image/_logos_partners/tesla-energy-certified.webp" alt="Tesla Energy Certified Installer" /></div>
        <div class="accreditation-logo"><img src="/image/_logos_partners/energy-safe-victoria.webp" alt="Energy Safe Victoria" /></div>
        <div class="accreditation-logo"><img src="/image/_logos_partners/solar-victoria.webp" alt="Solar Victoria" /></div>
        <div class="accreditation-logo accreditation-logo--large"><img src="/image/_logos_partners/enphase.webp" alt="Enphase Silver Installer" /></div>
        <div class="accreditation-logo accreditation-logo--large"><img src="/image/_logos_partners/newenergytech_approvaed seller.webp" alt="New Energy Tech Approved Seller" /></div>
        <div class="accreditation-logo accreditation-logo--medium"><img src="/image/_logos_partners/sigenergy-certified-installer.webp" alt="Sigenergy Certified Installer" /></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── CTA ── -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-inner">
        <h2>Let's talk about your home</h2>
        <p>We'd love to sit down, look at your energy data, and show you what's possible. No obligation, no pressure.</p>
        <a href="/services/consultation" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Free Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <ScrollIndicator />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ── Force solid dark nav on white page ── */
  :global(.header-v2::before) {
    background: rgba(14, 43, 71, 0.95) !important;
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) !important;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) !important;
    backdrop-filter: none !important;
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: none !important;
  }

  /* ── Hero ── */
  .about-hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 70vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
  }

  .about-hero-bg img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 40%;
  }

  .about-hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to top,
      rgba(14, 43, 71, 0.92) 0%,
      rgba(14, 43, 71, 0.6) 40%,
      rgba(14, 43, 71, 0.3) 100%
    );
  }

  .about-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 1rem 5rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .about-hero-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: #C2D456;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-hero h1 {
    font-size: 3.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }

  .hero-accent {
    color: #C2D456;
  }

  .about-hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
    max-width: 480px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .about-hero-wave {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: 45%;
    opacity: 0.06;
    z-index: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* ── Intro stat strip ── */
  .intro-strip {
    background: #0E2B47;
    padding: 0;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 3;
  }

  .intro-strip-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  }

  .intro-stat {
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }

  .intro-stat:last-child {
    border-right: none;
  }

  .intro-stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #C2D456;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .intro-stat-label {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    line-height: 1.4;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* ── Our Story ── */
  .story-section {
    padding: 6rem 0 4rem;
    background: #fff;
  }

  .story-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .story-col-left .section-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: #0E2B47;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .story-col-left h2 {
    font-size: 2.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0E2B47;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .story-lead {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #0E2B47;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .story-col-right p {
    color: #444;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .story-col-right p strong {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0E2B47;
  }

  .story-photos {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .story-photo {
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .story-photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .story-photo--wide img {
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
  }

  .story-photo--tall img {
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
  }

  /* ── What Makes Us Different ── */
  .difference-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: #f7f8f4;
  }

  .difference-header {
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .section-label--light {
    color: #0E2B47 !important;
  }

  .difference-header .section-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: #0E2B47;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .difference-header h2 {
    font-size: 2.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0E2B47;
    line-height: 1.2;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .difference-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .difference-card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem 1.75rem;
    border: 1px solid #e8e9e4;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }

  .difference-card:hover {
    border-color: #C2D456;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .difference-number {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #C2D456;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .difference-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0E2B47;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .difference-card p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* ── Team ── */
  .team-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: #fff;
  }

  .team-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .team-header .section-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: #0E2B47;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .team-header h2 {
    font-size: 2.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0E2B47;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .team-intro {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #555;
    max-width: 560px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .team-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .team-card {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .team-card-photo {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e9eee0 0%, #f0f1ec 100%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    min-height: 200px;
  }

  .team-card-photo img {
    width: 160px;
    height: 160px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top center;
  }

  .team-card-info {
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .team-card-info h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0E2B47;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .team-role {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: #2061B7;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .team-card-info > p:last-child {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ── Accreditations ── */
  .accreditations-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: #f8f9fa;
  }

  .accreditations-section .section-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: #0E2B47;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .accreditations-heading {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0E2B47;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .accreditations-logos {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, auto);
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2.5rem 3rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .accreditation-logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .accreditation-logo img {
    height: 52px;
    width: auto;
    max-width: none;
    opacity: 0.8;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
  }

  .accreditation-logo--large img {
    height: 85px;
  }

  .accreditation-logo--medium img {
    height: 65px;
  }

  .accreditation-logo img:hover {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  /* ── CTA ── */
  .cta-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: #0E2B47;
  }

  .cta-inner {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-inner h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .cta-inner p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.4rem;
    }

    .story-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .story-col-left h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }

    .story-photos {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .difference-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .team-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .intro-strip-inner {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .intro-stat {
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    }

    .intro-stat:nth-child(2) {
      border-right: none;
    }

    .intro-stat:nth-last-child(-n+2) {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .about-hero {
      min-height: 55vh;
    }

    .about-hero h1 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }

    .about-hero-content {
      padding: 3rem 1rem 3.5rem;
    }

    .story-section {
      padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
    }

    .story-col-left h2 {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
    }

    .story-photos {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .story-photo--tall img {
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    }

    .difference-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .difference-header h2 {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
    }

    .team-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .intro-strip-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .accreditations-logos {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 2rem;
      max-width: 500px;
    }

    .cta-inner h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
